Tracy, Respondent, v. Byrnes, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Labbemobe, C. J., and Daly and Van Hoesen, JJ.

Thos. J. McKee, for appellant. W. C. Campbell, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs and disbursements.
